+    /// re-quantize pass provably complete (every row is wholly before or
+    /// after the unique pin tx, so none can survive un-centered). Embedding
+    /// (`run_projection_job`) runs OUTSIDE the gate and stays parallel.
+    commit_gate: Mutex<()>,
 }
 
